# Hooks Organization

- Define hooks at the top of the component body
- Group hooks by functionality:
  1. State hooks (useState)
  2. Context hooks (useContext)
  3. Ref hooks (useRef)
  4. Effect hooks (useEffect)
  5. Callback hooks (useCallback)
  6. Memoization hooks (useMemo)
- Custom hooks should be prefixed with 'use'
- Extract complex logic into custom hooks
